summary: I both love and hate the Heaven sequences because on one hand they’re filmed incredibly uncomfortable (but I also kinda like...
caption:
I both love and hate the Heaven sequences because on one hand they’re filmed incredibly uncomfortable (but I also kinda like that because it makes sense) but on the other hand Michael’s eyes look absolutely stunning in this lighting

Can’t really tell what color his eyes are, though. They’re like.. blue, but also kinda brown? A golden-ish brown? Either way, I just wanted to point out how well his eyes actually matches his color scheme in his outfits, the gold, the browns and the light blue of his shirt

Nice job, Michael
